{"tid":889163,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"女人真係好小氣，包括啊媽","createTime":"2018-11-04T10:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T12:01:10.000Z","uid":24971,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1732624a77d01db3e412a45e141e65f9ff532ccc","tid":889163,"uid":24971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:48:14.000Z","msg":"話說閣下老母同天下母親一樣咁錫自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毫不吝嗇<br />\n<br />\n但早兩日天氣轉涼 開始乾燥<br />\n<br />\n我見塊面乾乾地 咪拎佢啲護膚野係咁易搽少少<br />\n<br />\n我一撻上塊面，佢即刻一句：屌你個衰仔你做乜野啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後遞咗支唔知乜野雜物牌保濕 <br />\n<br />\n仲要閪口閪面咁對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搽你少少野啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f018f3fac956eb588b3898755e6813858029acc","tid":889163,"uid":77643,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"閣下？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023c63b0df010d6995513706c8cac8109057719d","tid":889163,"uid":120466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa8d0615250063a6809675c452b31cfc9d49356","tid":889163,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T11:54:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b85ac3988905a8437e90d0784ab9d65fadc5cf","tid":889163,"uid":100321,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3f018f3fac956eb588b3898755e6813858029acc","tid":889163,"uid":77643,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy"